          "reviewBody": "This is one of the worst schools of faridabad actually it is so downgraded that the environment it provides destroy the mind of children there is zero communication and teacher treat students very brutely... teachers always do gender discrimination that's why there is so much of bad conversation skills among students...this school is more like some 80s or 90s type govt school...and yeah if we talk about facilities there literally nothing...no sports activity, no mun, no proper facilities in classrooms....teachers here are so illiterate...I will not even recommend this school to anyone.... dynasty intl school is lacking behind among all the modern schools nowadays....there should be change...the teachers should be replaced....this school is literally destroying the mindset of youth...*NOT recommended* ",
