            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I'm impressed with the school's commitment to providing a well-rounded education. The teachers are dedicated, enthusiastic, and maintain excellent communication with parents. The school's focus on holistic development aligns with our family's values.\n\nThe school's facilities are well-maintained, and the extracurricular activities have helped my child develop new skills and interests. The administration is approachable, and concerns are addressed promptly.",
          "publisher": {
