          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "From zenith to nadir, this school has downgraded in last few years especially after the demise of Smt. Bimla Varma.\n1. Let me quote an example: Teachers of class 5 and 6 do not check homework notebooks.They don't complete the course but give that in syllabus of exams.\nHow can a teacher of class 5,6,7 don't pay any heed to homework they give. This fact can be verified from any student.\nThis is one of the few examples...but quality has downgraded so quickly.\n2. No sports infrastructure.\n3. Frequent teacher change.\n4. Low quality staff.\n5. No effect of any suggestion.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Dynasty International School - Sector 28"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Priyank Kapur"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-09-13",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Our experience at Dynasty has been exceptional. The teachers are truly invested in my child’s education and her growth as a learner. Adjustments are made as needed to meet the needs of the student. Also, the teachers are super supportive and amazing. I’ve never worried about my child while she is under their care and guidance. They are not just teaching but nurturing my child.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Dynasty International School - Sector 28"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "romita shaw"
          },
          "datePublished": "2024-09-13",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Hello all,\nI am a single parent and my kid has been studying over here since class 1st, now in 6th. So it is a nice experience with all the staffs. Main thing is that every teacher have been so cooperative and helpful to my kid. I look forward that my child completes her 12th from here. The location is closed and very convenient to reach from the highway and from the inside area of sec 28. Everyone is really helpful...including drivers as well....to drop your kid safely. Fee structure is also affordable.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
